title: 55: Tech's Most Surprising Comeback
description:
Today on The Readback, we're switching things around a little. Guest host Jeffrey Cane interviews Alex Eule about his recent column on Garmin-a tech company that has found success far from Silicon Valley. The Readback is a weekly, finance and business podcast from Barron's. Producer: Mette Lützhøft. Published 11.06.2019.
